  "common": {
    "name": {
      "zh": "HK 417 7.62x51毫米突击步枪",
      "en": "HK 417 7.62x51 assault rifle"
    },
    "shortName": {
      "zh": "HK417",
      "en": "HK417"
    },
    "description": {
      "zh": "HK417是一款采用7.62x51毫米北约弹药的重型全自动突击步枪，以步兵武器的理想混合形态填补了突击步枪与狙击枪之间的火力空白。这款间接导气式武器根据弹药类型和枪管长度的不同，可在该口径下实现2500至3100焦耳的能量输出，其枪口动能足以支持与500米开外的目标交战。",
      "en": "The HK417 is a heavy, fully automatic assault rifle in 7.62x51mm NATO that closes the gap between assault and sniper rifles in the ideal mixture of infantry weapons. The indirect gas-operated weapon achieves energy values of 2500 to 3100 joules in its calibre, depending on ammunition and barrel length. Sufficient energy to effectively engage targets beyond 500 metres."
    },
